Revision history for Perl extension X11::Terminal.

1.0.0  2013/05/06 Semantic versioning (www.semver.org)
                  Use more "standard" filenames
                  Changes to allow building under newer OS

0.4    2011/06/24 Update Documentation
                  Convert to Module::Build

0.3    2010/06/27 Include version in every .pm file

0.2    2010/06/27 Add scrollback option (for XTerm)
                  Add support for Konsole
                  Documentation corrections

0.01   2010/05/27 Original version.
